{"3378270": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Love&Bitch", "steam_appid": 3378270, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◼︎ <strong>遊戲介紹</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/676c38d25b04a069a6364c745a2a7f42.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >獻給所有喜歡NTR的人ーー<br>這不是普通的NTR遊戲，而是<strong>「<u>超</u>」NTR遊戲</strong>！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不管做什麼都會被NTR！什麼都不做也照樣會被NTR！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升等級、好感度、賺錢……等等。<br>一切和搞黃色無關的多餘要素全部捨棄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要做的只有「欣賞色情事件」，只有這樣而已！<br>請盡情享受這個只有色色的超級特化型色情遊戲吧！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◼︎ <strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與嚮往的前輩悠香結婚後，我原本以為會過著恩恩愛愛的兩人生活。<br>卻在某日我被上司告知悠香挪用了公款，甚至也簽屬了願意以AV出道來還債的荒謬契約。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在上司的要求下，我也加入了AV還債的一環。<br>然而，我能做的卻只是看著電腦螢幕，默默剪輯著自己的老婆不斷地被人抽插的影片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這樣的<strong><u>扭曲的日常</u></strong>，恐怕得持續到<strong><u>還完3000萬日圓</u></strong>的那一天吧……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◼︎ <strong>角色介紹 </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/ab4c3b6b7e09c759fe6a576713c1a562.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◼︎ <strong>豐富多樣的色情事件</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/f9a5957b8915ddff9ff5463a1d0ae836.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【強○AV攝影事件】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讓心愛的妻子被NTR來賺錢的事件。<br>可以從社長、黑人或專業AV男優三人中選擇一名來做竿役。<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/ad2186cbe656bb5cb4335157c1ce2cce.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【週末NTR事件】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中在週六&amp;週日（Day6或Day13等等）女主角可能會不在…… <br>至於她是去跟誰幽會，就取決於各位的選擇了。 <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/29b7894d3ea1620f4b9ed76e0e8413b5.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【日常NTR事件（公司）】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >經過第一次的週末NTR事件後，在職場裡也產生了一些變化！？<br>根據劇情進展狀況，竿役或許會跟女主角……<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/bd1588e812e3608bb2614653c2d53e12.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>【日常NTR事件（自家）】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >發生變化的不只有職場！？在家裡，妻子會跟外遇對象們……<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/8b2572943ca732acacf864b90d4af441.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【夫妻愛事件】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要在自己家裡和女主角搭話就會觸發事件。 <br>究竟洋一能不能作為丈夫取回妻子的愛呢……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/a6b8c9835243a04e189c6544ef4c93cf.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=400 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【結局】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有共4種的複數結局分歧。<br>親眼見證各竿役的結局，以及真正的NTR結局吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>  </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◼︎ <strong>回想模式</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/47950f3b26ac3b51eb410502c737f481.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=390 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從「強○AV攝影事件」到「結局」都能夠輕鬆閱覽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特別推薦給雖然想玩但沒時間的忙碌上班族！<br>實裝了可以回顧本篇中所有色情事件的回想模式！<br>除此之外也實裝了「全事件開放開關」，買下遊戲後馬上就可以享受所有色情事件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◼︎ 概要</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >總CG高達「200張」的超豐富內容！！（※含差分21張）<br>色情事件數量超過了驚人的「100個」！！<br>同時具備讓色情事件更加生動誘人的BGS（呻吟、高潮聲、喔齁聲）！！</p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◼︎ <strong>遊戲介紹</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/676c38d25b04a069a6364c745a2a7f42.avif?t=1767924394\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >獻給所有喜歡NTR的人ーー<br>這不是普通的NTR遊戲，而是<strong>「<u>超</u>」NTR遊戲</strong>！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不管做什麼都會被NTR！什麼都不做也照樣會被NTR！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升等級、好感度、賺錢……等等。<br>一切和搞黃色無關的多餘要素全部捨棄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要做的只有「欣賞色情事件」，只有這樣而已！<br>請盡情享受這個只有色色的超級特化型色情遊戲吧！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◼︎ <strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與嚮往的前輩悠香結婚後，我原本以為會過著恩恩愛愛的兩人生活。<br>卻在某日我被上司告知悠香挪用了公款，甚至也簽屬了願意以AV出道來還債的荒謬契約。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在上司的要求下，我也加入了AV還債的一環。<br>然而，我能做的卻只是看著電腦螢幕，默默剪輯著自己的老婆不斷地被人抽插的影片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這樣的<strong><u>扭曲的日常</u></strong>，恐怕得持續到<strong><u>還完3000萬日圓</u></strong>的那一天吧……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◼︎ <strong>角色介紹 </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378270/extras/ab4c3b6b7e09c759fe6a576713c1a562.a